channel.title: [317] Royalscape Revolutionz [Delta] 400+ Downloads!
channel.description:
[center][size=36pt]RoyalScape Revolutionz[/size] [size=24pt]PLEASE LEAVE SUGGESTIONS IF I SHOULD MAKE V2[/size][/center]
This is a pretty simple Delta based server that i started coding probably around 3-4 months ago, I stopped coding it and am releasing it today as it was distracting me from my school work to much. I was hosting it for probaly around 2 months and if I still could, then I would. I hope you guys enjoy it as much as i did. Thanks!! P.S. please don't hate on the background of the client, I don't have Photoshop or any good image editing tools.
[b][u]Things that could be worked on[/u][/b]
[ul][li]Adding more bosses[/li] [li]More drops to monsters[/li] [li]New Login screen[/li] [li]Adding more customs[/li] [li]Fixing some minor glitches[/li] [li]Fixing some of the skills that are glitched[/li][/ul]
[b][u]Things already done or working[/u][/b] [color=limegreen][size=10pt]
[ul][li]Working Godwars[/li] [li]Working Pest Control[/li] [li]Working Barrows[/li] [li]Delta Based[/li] [li]Safe Wild[/li] [li]Almost Perfect Skilling[/li] [li]King Black Dragon[/li] [li]Mith Drags[/li] [li]Working Dragon Claws[/li] [li]All Godswords With Working Specs[/li] [li]Barbarian Assault[/li] [li]Fight Caves[/li] [li]Clue Scrolls[/li] [li]Tons Of Customs[/li] [li]Working Vengeance [/li] [li]Working Sara Sword[/li] [li]Working Quests[/li] [li]Winter Weather[/li] [li]Kalphite Queen[/li] [li]Giant Mole[/li] [li]Working Warriors Guild[/li][/ul]
